<p>The Sharks were not careful with the puck last night. NHL.com reports that San Jose had 22 giveaways to Detroit’s 11 and just two takeaways to Detroit’s five. </p>



<p>At least two of those giveaways led to goals in the other direction, such as the Red Wings’ second goal. </p>



