<p>The second period is where the Knights did most of their damage, scoring 3 goals to go up 5-2. Timothy Liljegren made a great play to cut the lead to 3 before the period was over, pinching at the perfect time to catch a flying puck before sending it to Wennberg for a one-timer goal.&nbsp;</p>



